8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%B1%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to free, to liberate, to emancipate","examples":[{"text":"وَمَنْ قَتَلَ مُؤْمِنًا خَطَأً فَتَحْرِيرُ رَقَبَةٍ مُؤْمِنَةٍ","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to devote to the service of religion"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to examine minutely"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to verify"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to compose carefully, to write accurately"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make an accurate reckoning of"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to write"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to adjust"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to point or direct (a gun)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to revise (a book)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to edit"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to mercerize"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħar.ra.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7499","headword_ar":"حرّر","root":"Hr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHoriyrN","text_ar":"تَحْرِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He freed, liberated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emancipated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a slave. (A, Mgh, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr~r raqabapF","text_ar":"حرّر رَقَبَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He freed a neck"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"e. a slave"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He set apart"},{"kind":"text","text":"a child"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the worship of God and the service of the mosque or oratory:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he devoted"},{"kind":"text","text":"him"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the service of the church as long as he should live, so that he could not relinquish it while he retained his religion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, inf. n. as above, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made"},{"kind":"text","text":"a writing &c."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accurate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exact;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made"},{"kind":"text","text":"a writing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beautiful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegant, and free from defects, by forming its characters rightly, and rectifying its faults"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he wrote"},{"kind":"text","text":"a writing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegantly, and accurately,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exactly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TK;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he wrote well,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elegantly"},{"kind":"text","text":": (KL:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made"},{"kind":"text","text":"an account, or a reckoning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accurate, without mistake, and without omission, and without erasure."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [And simply (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wrote"},{"kind":"text","text":"a letter &c.]"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","A","KL"]}]}}